overview: When the dancers at the local strip club off the interstate, The Candy Bank, start disappearing, only a gang of fearless heroines have what it takes to settle the score. Sexy rock-n-rollers by day, lethal, blood-thirsty vigilantes by night, L'Assassins are on the prowl. They're going deep undercover to catch a killer, and make him pay. Their only code is KILL! KILL! KILL!
title: L'Assassins
